

How it all works: 

Created a database that will list all of the abilities in the video game: valorant
They will be normalized in third-form normalization. 

The first table listing the abilities name and cost. 
    This will help with stating what the abilities are before categorizing them further with other sections.

The second table will state the agents name and role. 

The third table will associate abilities with their respective agents. 
    This table will be used the most going forward as this will help with stating the abilities and agents relationship.



Upon this point, we have reached the categorization labeling of the abilities